use of coral bleaching. Coral bleaching occurs when corals become stressed by negative changes in conditions. This causes them to lose their beautiful colors and turn completely white. If this continues, the coral will eventually die. Reefs worldwide, including the Great Barrier Reef in Australia, have been affected hugely by coral bleaching.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7.jpg\" alt=\"reef safe sunscreen\"><\/noscript><img width=\"428\" height=\"338\" alt=\"reef safe sunscreen\" class=\"wp-image-56275 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-759x600.jpg 759w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-1025x810.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-428x338.jpg 428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-163x129.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-228x180.jpg 228w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-768x607.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-1024x809.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103914\/reef-safe-sunscreen7-1367x1080.jpg 1367w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/