s\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"maldives\" class=\"wp-image-56281 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives-24x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23104951\/maldives.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-why-is-coral-important\">Why is Coral Important?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We must protect and care for coral, as it generates nearly 50% of the world&#x2019;s oxygen! Not only that, but coral reefs act as a habitat for around 25% of the world&#x2019;s marine species. Fish and other marine life have less food and places to live when corals get damaged. The effect of this is a reduction in marine life, which can cause fishing and tourism problems, something that many coastal communities rely on for their economy.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Did you know?<\/strong> The reef also acts as a natural barrier to prevent flooding.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/sustainable-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to Travel more Sustainable<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103832\/reef-safe-sunscreen3.jpg\" alt=\"reef safe sunscreen\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"reef safe sunscreen\" class=\"wp-image-56266 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103832\/reef-safe-sunscreen3.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/