afe Sunscreen and what ingredients to avoid?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The three main ingredients to watch out for in your sunscreen are Oxybenzone, Octinoxate, and Octocrylene. These are all popular ingredients that are believed to contribute highly to coral bleaching. Because of this, countries like Hawaii and Palau have banned these ingredients. (applause!) <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8.jpg\" alt=\"reef safe sunscreen\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"reef safe sunscreen\" class=\"wp-image-56277 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1427px) 100vw, 1427px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8.jpg 1427w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-446x600.jpg 446w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-602x810.jpg 602w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-251x338.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-134x180.jpg 134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-571x768.jpg 571w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-761x1024.jpg 761w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/23103926\/reef-safe-sunscreen8-803x1080.jpg 803w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/up